"16:8:4" : {s: 16, a: 8, w: 4, r: "ركب", t: "لِتَرْكَبُوهَا", l: "رَكِبَ", lc: 9, tl: "litarkabūhā", lb: "আরোহণ করা",e: "for you to ride them", b: "", i: "agar kamu menungganginya", f: 1, rm: "to ride, embark, mount, be carried, go on board of a ship, voyage on (the sea), walk on (a road), commit (a fault). rakbun - caravan. rukban (pl. of rakib) - one who rides, mounted. rikab - camels. rakub - use of a beast for riding. mutarakibun - laying in heaps, ridden on one another, close growing, cluster over clustered, layer upon layer. tarkabunna - to pass on, rise, ascend.", ag: "لام التعليل وفعل مضارع وضمير متصل وضمير متصل ", eg: "Purposive lām and Verb Imperfect and Pronoun suffix and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "SUBJ", lu: "ٱرْكَب"},
"16:8:5" : {s: 16, a: 8, w: 5, r: "زين", t: "وَزِينَةًۭ", l: "زِينَة", lc: 19, tl: "wazīnatan", lb: "সৌন্দর্য, শোভা, সাজ, সজ্জা, অলঙ্কার",e: "and (as) adornment", b: "", i: "dan perhiasan", f: 1, rm: "To adorn, deck. Adorn, grace, honor [said of an action, quality, or saying]. Embellished, dressed, or trimmed it [relating to language]. Adorned [ex. The earth, or land, became adorned with or by its herbage], ornamented, decorated, decked, bedecked, garnished, embellished, beautified, or graced him/it. Of language it is said: It was embellished, dressed up, or trimmed. Of action it is said: It was embellished, dressed up; i.e. commended to a person by another man. A grace, a beauty, a comely quality, a physical/intellectual adornment, an honour or a credit, and anything that is the pride or glory of a person or a thing. A thing that does not disgrace or render unseemly a wise man in any of his states or conditions, either in the present world or in that which is to come. It [states] are of three kinds: Mental: Such as knowledge/science and good tenants. Bodily: Strength, tallness of stature, beauty of aspect. Extrinsic: Wealth, rank or station, dignity.", ag: "واو عطف وأسم نكرة", eg: "Conjunction wa and Noun Indefinite state", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "INDEF", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "", mood: "", lu: "زَيَّنَ،زُيِّنَ،زِينَةُ"},
